    <h3>Apiary Management Routes (Controller::Apiary — members only)</h3>
    <div class="content-section">
        <p>See <a href="/Documentation/controllers/Apiary">Apiary Controller Documentation</a> for the full route list. Key routes:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><a href="/Apiary"><code>/Apiary</code></a> — member apiary dashboard</li>
            <li><code>/Apiary/HiveManagement</code> — hive management</li>
            <li><code>/Apiary/QueenRearing</code> — queen rearing system</li>
            <li><code>/Apiary/BeeHealth</code> — colony health monitoring</li>
            <li><code>/Apiary/inspections</code> — hive inspection records</li>
            <li><code>/Apiary/inspections/new</code> — new inspection form</li>
            <li><code>/Apiary/inspections/calendar</code> — inspection calendar</li>
            <li><code>/Apiary/inspections/reports</code> — seasonal reports</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
</div>

