                    <td><code>Model::BeekeepingModel</code></td>
                    <td>Yard and hive-list helpers for the Beekeeping controller hierarchy. Methods: <code>get_yards_for_site($c, $sitename)</code>, <code>get_hives_for_yard($c, $yard_id)</code>, <code>create_yard($c, \%params)</code>.</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td><code>Model::ApiaryModel</code></td>
